    "en": {
      "title": "In New York, a baby was shot dead while holding a baby",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In New York City, USA, a young woman was shot in the head and killed by a young man who was traveling in a cart.",
        "The attacker did not harm the child, and police say the suspect fled after the shooting.",
        "However, the women who were shot died on the spot and the police have already launched an operation to nab the suspect.",
        "With the free use of firearms in the United States, there has been an increase in the number of homicides reported in the United States over the past year."
